<p>Suburban areas like Upper Arlington, Worthington, and Dublin typically offer ideal conditions for residential solar with newer homes, optimal roof orientations, and fewer shading issues. These neighborhoods' larger homes averaging 2000+ sq ft benefit most from comprehensive solar-HVAC integration. Clintonville and Grandview Heights present mixed opportunities with diverse housing stock ranging from older homes needing full HVAC replacement to newer construction ready for solar integration.</p>

